 A young lady has taken to weeping bitterly for days after she was left heartbroken by her supposed long-time boyfriend. Reports claim that the lady had been in a series of relationship this year and all had come to a devastating end. It is no doubt that heartbreaks can be a very terrible experience which sometimes leaves one crying uncontrollably; the lady in the viral video must have loved her partner dearly as she could be seen crying unceasingly.
The lady feels that she has some sort of bad luck with love after all the relationship she’s been in sunk in less than a year. In the video making the rounds online, the lady could be seen crying bitterly on different days as her roommates and friends kept consoling her. WATCH VIDEO